migrations/*.backup

# API keys and secrets (extra safety)
*_API_KEY*
*_SECRET*
credentials.json
secrets.json
# ...but the safety globs must never swallow real source files: on a
# case-insensitive checkout (macOS/Windows) `*_SECRET*` matches the
# secret-guard TEST module, which broke the public release export
# (fresh clone -> untracked -> git add refused). Re-include explicitly.
!tests/unit/agents/task/core/test_secret_guard.py

